name: High Jump
requires: |Triple Jump| or |Back Flip| or |Side Flip| or (|Ground Pound| and |Ground Pound Jump|)

name: Pyramid Skip
requires: |Bullet Bill| or ((|Long Jump| or |Triple Jump|) + Cap Vault)

name: Into the Lake
requires: (|Zipper| and |Swim|) or (|Cap Vault| and (|High Jump| OR |Long Jump| OR (|Triple Jump| AND |Wall Jump|))) OR (|Cap Jump| AND |Triple Jump| AND |Wall Jump| AND |Goomba|)

name: Sherm Wall
requires: (|Hold/Throw| or (|High Jump| and |Cap Vault|) or (|Uproot| and |Dive|)) and (|Sherm| or (|Goomba| and |Wall Jump| and |Dive|))

name: Enter the Courtyard
requires: |Pokio| or (|Dive| and ((|Ground Pound Jump| + |Ground Pound|) or |Backflip| or |Wall Jump|))

name: Parabones Skip
requires: |Parabones| or (|Cap Vault| and (|Long Jump| or |Triple Jump|))

name: Moon Cave Skip
requires: (|Back Flip| or (|Ground Pound| + |Ground Pound Jump|)) and |Cap Jump| and |Wall Jump|
